<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM5.1.10">
<l>kaṟṟā maṟittu kāḷiyaṉṟaṉ ceṉṉi naṭuṅka naṭampayiṉṟa</l>
<l>poṟṟā maraiyāḷ taṉkēḷvaṉ puḷḷam pūtaṅ kuṭitaṉmēl</l>
<l>kaṟṟār paravum maṅkaiyarkkōṉ kārār puyaṟkaik kalikaṉṟi</l>
<l>coltā ṉīrain tivaipāṭac cōra nillā tuyartāmē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>When [you] sing these twice-five [verses], the words of Kalikaṉṟi,</l>
<l rend="indent">whose hands are [as benevolent as] rain-filled clouds,</l>
<l>The king of those of Maṅkai, whom the learned praise,</l>
<l rend="indent">on Puḷḷampūtankuṭi</l>
<l>Of the lover of the lady on the golden lotus,</l>
<l rend="indent">who performed a dance so that Kāliya’s head shook,</l>
<l>Having stopped the cows with calves [from straying],</l>
<l rend="indent">suffering, so that [you] languish, cannot last.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
